</picture></div><p>A step-by-step guide to starting a coffee shop.</p></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section1" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>1.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=make-sure-you-understand-the-coffee-industry>Make sure you understand the coffee industry.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section1-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=decide-what-type-of-coffee-shop-you-want>Decide what type of coffee shop you want.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-decide-on-the-type-of-coffee-shop-you-want-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Decide what type of coffee shop you want."></div></div><p>Deciding on the perfect coffee shop business option is important as it will affect the level of income you can expect. When it comes to opening your own coffee shop, there are three basic options: buying an existing coffee shop, buying a coffee shop franchise, or starting from scratch.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Purchasing an existing coffee shop allows you access to a turnkey business. Almost everything is already sorted, and you wouldn’t need to do many alterations, especially if the business was thriving before the sale.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Purchasing a coffee shop franchise means that most of your business decisions will be made for you, but you'll have a turnkey business.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Starting your coffee shop from scratch requires the most effort and work, but it also provides the most flexibility and the best potential to maximize profits.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section1-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=research-the-coffee-market>Research the coffee market.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-research-the-coffee-market-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Research the coffee market."></div></div><p>The process of researching trends, competitors, and equipment is critical. There are many consultancies and professionals that offer advice to help you through this process. However, business consultants cost between $50.00 and $300.00 per hour.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Start doing market research on your own by building relationships with current or previous coffee shop owners. Learn from their experiences, mistakes, and training.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Visit various coffee shops in and around your city and learn where they differ. In the end, you’ll want to search for a gap in the market.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Learn everything you can about the 1,000s of flavonoids that make up the taste of coffee. Coffee can be complex to make and there are many ways for it to go wrong. But these variables also mean that there are many delicious roasting profiles and blends that are waiting to be discovered by your customer's taste buds.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>You can study the art of coffee through books, events, seminars, and coffee tastings. This is also a great way to meet fellow coffee lovers and professionals in the coffee industry.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section1-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=learn-about-coffee-roasters>Learn about coffee roasters.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-learn-about-coffee-roasters-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Learn about coffee roasters."></div></div><p>When opening your own business, you will be faced with two options: to roast your own coffee beans or to find a coffee roaster who will deliver. Learning to roast your own coffee beans will require tons of training and development, but it is an investment you'll want to consider. If you wish to have your beans delivered, then consider local or corporate roasters.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Roasting will save you money in the long run, but getting started will require additional capital. This will include extra money for roasting equipment, installation, purchasing beans, and training staff.</p></div><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Visit local coffee shops and try their various blends. If you find a few that you like, buy a bag and take it to your local roaster. Ask the professionals what their wholesale cost is per pound and what type of support they would provide if you sold and advertised their brand.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section2" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>2.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=write-a-business-plan>Write a business plan.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section2-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=start-by-creating-a-business-plan-overview>Start by creating a business plan overview.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-business-plan-288x288-20200723.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Start by creating a business plan overview."></div></div><p>This will help you get a clear picture of what you want your coffee shop to offer. This business plan does not need to be the traditional, lengthy version you'll use when searching for funding. You can create an overview that summarizes the ideas you have.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section2-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=determine-your-business-concept>Determine your business concept.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-determine-your-business-concept-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Determine your business concept."></div></div><p>What type of coffee shop do you want? Do you want to open a coffee stand or a storefront? When developing your business plan, it's important to have your business concept laid out. This step allows you to turn your business dreams into a concept on paper - which may help investors understand what you're trying to build.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>While you complete your research and visit various coffee shops, jot down interesting offers and designs you've noticed. These will help you find trends.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section2-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=develop-an-understanding-of-your-usp>Develop an understanding of your USP.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-understand-your-usp-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Develop an understanding of your USP."></div></div><p>As a coffee business owner, you will need to find your 'edge' or the 'thing' that makes your coffee shop special. Start by developing an understanding of your competitive position and what your unique selling proposition will be.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Your USP is something that you should evaluate throughout this process.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section2-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>2.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=refine-your-coffee-shop-business-plan>Refine your coffee shop business plan.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-work-on-your-coffee-shop-business-plan-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Refine your coffee shop business plan."></div></div><p>This will ensure you're ready to give your plan to the owner or property manager of your future coffee shop location. Update your overview regularly and ensure that all your ideas are evaluated over time.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Start with an executive summary. This should include a summary of your business, location, size, company ownership, objectives, and strategies.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>You will need a market analysis to show that you have a good understanding of the coffee market. This should list the trends, target market, and data you researched.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Add a competitive analysis that includes information about your current and future local competitors. List the strengths and weaknesses of your competitors, and how you will make a difference.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Compose a section on your product line. This should include a list of the products you plan on offering. Add your menu and the potential costs of each item, as well as the vendors you plan on using.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Plan out your management strategy. This should include a layout of your management team, responsibilities, and employee costs.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Lastly, lay out your financial considerations, costs, and financial strategies. It's important that you list how you would fund your business in detail.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section3" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>3.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=find-your-ideal-location>Find your ideal location.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section3-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=look-into-various-types-of-locations>Look into various types of locations.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-choose-a-location-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Look into various types of locations."></div></div><p>Your ideal location should be convenient, highly visible, and on a busy street with plenty of parking. This way, customers can easily drop in on their way to or from work, gym, or school.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>A shopping mall can give you access to thousands of shoppers, but there may also be a lot of competition, rent may be higher, and you may not have complete control over your business hours. These restrictions are important factors to consider.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>A storefront location is harder to find but can offer fewer restrictions. Depending on your location, storefronts offer visibility, negotiable rent, and you can set your own business hours.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>A drive-thru coffee shop serves a dual purpose when joined with a regular coffee shop. They offer quick service and convenience. Customers on their way to work prefer a quick stop and wouldn’t want to stand in long lines. These locations should have high-visibility and good drive-thru space.</p></div><div
class="step-direction tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>When searching for a location, parking and traffic play a vital role in finding the perfect spot. Unless you decide to locate your coffee shop in a mall or other high-pedestrian traffic site, your location needs to be easily accessible and provide adequate parking.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section3-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=sign-a-lease-agreement>Sign a lease agreement.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-sign-a-lease-agreement-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Sign a lease agreement."></div></div><p>Make sure that you have read through the entire contract, word for word, and that you understand all the terms and how they will impact you. While reading through the contract, make a list of any provisions you don't agree with and send the list with possible amendments to the landlord to negotiate the best deal possible.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Check that the lease is assignable, meaning that you if you decide to sell your coffee shop, the new owner can take over the lease. If the lease is not assignable, the landlord will have the right the cancel the lease agreement, which will negatively impact the sale of your business.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section4" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>4.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=decide-on-a-coffee-shop-menu-and-prepare-your-finances>Decide on a coffee shop menu and prepare your finances.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section4-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>4.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=write-down-a-basic-list-of-all-the-items-you-wish-to-market>Write down a basic list of all the items you wish to market.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-decide-on-a-menu-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Write down a basic list of all the items you wish to market."></div></div><p>Developing a menu for your coffee shop will play a central part in your business planning. Without it, you won't identify your equipment needs, estimated budget, space requirements, or even location. Spend a good amount of time researching options that will boost sales.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section4-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>4.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=calculate-your-start-up-costs>Calculate your start-up costs.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-calculate-your-startup-costs-288x288-20200728_2023-09-25-003227_cojp.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Calculate your start-up costs."></div></div><p>Starting a coffee shop business from scratch is a sizable investment. The amount of funding you will need depends on your coffee shop's size, food services, location, equipment, and other variables.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>It is vital to determine your start-up costs before making any big moves. Start by planning your menu, creating your concept, researching equipment cost, and scouting locations. Once you have these elements, you can develop a realistic budget.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section4-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>4.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=calculate-your-break-even-point>Calculate your break-even point.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-calculate-break-even-point-288x288-20200723.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Calculate your break-even point."></div></div><p>Your break-even point is the point at which your total cost and total revenue are equal. Knowing your break-even point is vital, especially for start-up businesses that will need to identify their sales goals.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Calculating your break-even point will determine what sales volume is necessary to cover costs.</p></div><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Leave room for surprises. Some things may cost less than expected, others more. Plan on spending about 20% more than expected to give yourself some room to breathe in cases of emergency.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section4-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>4.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=understand-your-cost-per-item-sold-metrics>Understand your Cost Per Item Sold metrics.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-understand-cost-per-item-sold-metrics-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Understand your Cost Per Item Sold metrics."></div></div><p>Cost Per Item Sold metrics will help you to determine prices, what kinds of discounts you can offer, and what it costs to give away a free cup of coffee. Your costs will be based on the different types of products served and on the quantity that goes into each item.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Have a look at our examples of Cost Per Item Sold metrics at the bottom of this page.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section5" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>5.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=obtain-funding-for-your-coffee-shop>Obtain funding for your coffee shop.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section5-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=ask-family-and-friends>Ask family and friends.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-ask-family-and-friends-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Ask family and friends."></div></div><p>Start by discussing your business plan with friends and family. Plan and present a well-researched business plan and ask them to invest in your business.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section5-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-a-loan>Apply for a loan.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-a-loan-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for a loan."></div></div><p>If you're unable to obtain funding through family, or if you need more cash than your family can provide, start looking into local loan options. In many cases, cities will offer business assistance programs to offset costs.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section5-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=look-into-crowdfunding>Look into crowdfunding.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-look-into-crowdfunding-288x288-20200821.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Look into crowdfunding."></div></div><p>You can raise money for your coffee business by appealing to the online community and asking for financial assistance. Crowdfunding is an excellent way to fund a project without giving up equity or accumulating debt.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Funds are usually used in exchange for gifts, future products, or other small rewards. However, crowdfunding does require continuous marketing and patience.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section5-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=start-small>Start small.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-start-small-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Start small."></div></div><p>Starting a major coffee shop from scratch might not be an option for everyone. Consider starting small by opening a coffee stand, truck, or cart. This option is much more affordable.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>It can cost between $15,000 and $100,000 to start a coffee stand.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section5-step5" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>5.5&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-an-sba-backed-loan-local-bank-or-credit-union>Apply for an SBA-backed loan, local bank, or credit union.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-an-sba-loan-288x288-20200724_2023-09-25-003855_zvqx.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for an SBA-backed loan, local bank, or credit union."></div></div><p>This process can be very personal as lenders will need to review your credit score. Very small loans (up to $50,000) have lower credit score requirements with a minimum of around 620-640+. This process will also depend on business factors including monthly revenue, cash flow, and time in business.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section6" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>6.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=research-and-comply-with-local-laws-and-regulations>Research and comply with local laws and regulations.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section6-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=obtain-a-business-license>Obtain a business license.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-check-the-us-small-business-administration-website-for-license-and-permit-requirements-for-your-location-288x288-20200727.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Obtain a business license."></div></div><p>Some states don’t require a general business license. However, you need to verify if your location requires specific licenses.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>To find out where to obtain your business license, Google your city’s name and business license.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>In addition, check the United States <a
href="https://www.sba.gov/">Small Business Administration</a> (SBA)’s website for more details.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>In some states, you can simply follow the application procedures laid out on your state government’s website or go to City Hall and request the proper documents.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section6-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=apply-for-a-food-service-license>Apply for a food service license.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apply-for-business-and-food-service-licenses-288x288-20200814_2023-09-25-004047_cvpm.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Apply for a food service license."></div></div><p>A food service license is issued by your local health department. This specific license will require a health department official to visit your location.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>The fees for a food service license are often based on the classification and size of your coffee shop, as well as where it’s located. It may also be based on the number of employees you have. But often the costs range from $100 to $1,000.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>To apply for a food service license, you must fill in the online application or collect an application at your local health department. Once you've filled in the form, submit it and continue the process, which includes a visit from a health department official.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>To ensure your kitchen meets health department standards, view the <a
href="https://www.fda.gov/food/fda-food-code/state-retail-and-food-service-codes-and-regulations-state">different states' rules and regulations</a>.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section6-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=decide-if-you-need-to-apply-for-a-food-handler-039-s-permit>Decide if you need to apply for a food handler&#039;s permit.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-consider-if-you-need-a-food-handlers-permit-288x288-20200817_2023-09-25-004223_spbc.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Decide if you need to apply for a food handler&#039;s permit."></div></div><p>If you’re planning on preparing your food in-house, you’ll likely need a food handler's permit to operate. Also referred to as a food handlers certificate, this document will guarantee that your coffee shop meets food sanitation, storage, protection, and preparation regulations.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Your employees will need to complete a state-approved food handler course and purchase a food handler’s permit. Depending on the state you live in, the cost of a food handler's permit can cost $100 to $500. This permit expires over a period of three to five years.</p></div><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>Consider hiring legal representation to help you navigate the legal side of starting a business and obtain the proper licensing and permits.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section7" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>7.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=set-up-you-business-operations>Set up you business operations.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section7-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=choose-your-business-structure>Choose your business structure.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-corporations-and-llcs-288x288-20200622.png?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Choose your business structure."></div></div><p>In the United States, most coffee shop owners will establish their businesses as LLCs. However, there are a few that are set up as partnerships and corporations. Determine what will best suit you and the type of business you’re trying to build.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section7-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-business-insurance>Get business insurance.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-obtain-business-insurance-288x288-20200812_2023-09-25-004410_dcqz.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get business insurance."></div></div><p>Obtaining insurance for your coffee business should be considered when planning finances. This step is often overlooked by coffee shop business owners even though it may be required to please banks, property managers, and investors. Ensure your business, employees, and assets are secure by investing in solid insurance.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>General liability insurance is a must-have for any business, especially coffee businesses that have frequent interactions with customers. It will protect you if your baristas, coffee, or any of your products cause harm to people.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Business property insurance will help protect your physical business property. Your insurance should include any outdoor or exterior property such as signage, railings, umbrellas, decks, and lighting.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Business income coverage may depend on your location and coffee business. However, it will help you keep your ability to pay for necessary fixed and variable expenses.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Equipment coverage is critical for your business because coffee equipment is expensive.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section7-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>7.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-an-employer-identification-number>Get an Employer Identification Number (EIN).</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-get-an-employer-identification-number-288x288-20200817_2023-09-25-004526_isou.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get an Employer Identification Number (EIN)."></div></div><p>Before you start hiring staff, you will need an employer identification number (EIN). Also referred to as the Federal Employer Identification Number (FEIN), this nine-digit number will act as a tax ID number.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>To receive your EIN quickly, <a
href="https://www.irs.gov/businesses/small-businesses-self-employed/apply-for-an-employer-identification-number-ein-online">applying online</a> is the best option.</p></div></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section8" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>8.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=recruit-quality-staff>Recruit quality staff.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section8-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=research-local-laws-and-wages-first>Research local laws and wages first.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-research-local-laws-and-wages-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Research local laws and wages first."></div></div><p>Depending on your state, there may be local minimum wage laws to consider. Check with the <a
href="https://www.dol.gov/general/topic/wages/minimumwage">Department of Labor</a> for minimum wage requirements.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
<path
d="M256,0C114.844,0,0,114.844,0,256s114.844,256,256,256s256-114.844,256-256S397.156,0,256,0z M298.667,416    c0,5.896-4.771,10.667-10.667,10.667h-64c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667V256h-10.667c-5.896,0-10.667-4.771-10.667-10.667    v-42.667c0-5.896,4.771-10.667,10.667-10.667H288c5.896,0,10.667,4.771,10.667,10.667V416z M256,170.667    c-23.531,0-42.667-19.135-42.667-42.667S232.469,85.333,256,85.333s42.667,19.135,42.667,42.667S279.531,170.667,256,170.667z" data-original="#000000" class="active-path" data-old_color="#000000" fill="#4949E7"/>
</g>
</svg>
</span><p>In the United States, the federal minimum wage is $7.25 an hour. However, this can vary by state. Most baristas and coffee attendants get paid the minimum wage of their state and can expect an average income of $19,000 - $30,000 per year.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section8-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=research-the-wages-for-all-positions>Research the wages for all positions.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-research-wages-for-all-positions-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Research the wages for all positions."></div></div><p>Depending on the type of coffee business you are building, you will need a range of employees to assist you. These may include a barista, waiter/waitress, busboy, baker, etc. Be aware of the wages each position expects. Some positions might require additional costs because of expertise and training.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section8-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=form-a-payroll-budget>Form a payroll budget.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-setup-payroll-for-your-staff-288x288-20200812_2023-09-25-004737_hteo.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Form a payroll budget."></div></div><p>This will help you to determine the sum total of compensation for your employees. This step may also help you to determine how many employees you can afford to hire.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section8-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=place-ads-in-local-newspapers-and-job-listing-websites>Place ads in local newspapers and job listing websites.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-advertise-your-vacancies-288x288-20200813_2023-09-25-004821_yycd.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Place ads in local newspapers and job listing websites."></div></div><p>Starting a business means you’ll be a source for local employment. Advertising in your city will be beneficial to your business and the community.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section8-step5" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>8.5&nbsp;</span><h4 id=hold-tryouts-for-positions-that-require-skills>Hold tryouts for positions that require skills.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hold-tryouts-for-skilled-positions-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Hold tryouts for positions that require skills."></div></div><p>While some positions might not require a wide set of skills, others will. Baristas and bakers are important positions to fill when starting a coffee shop. These employees need to be skilled and trained in their field. Before you hire employees, consider hosting tryouts to review their work.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section9" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>9.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=decide-on-an-accounting-system>Decide on an accounting system.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section9-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=weigh-the-pros-and-cons-of-hiring-an-accountant>Weigh the pros and cons of hiring an accountant.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-consider-hiring-an-accountant-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Weigh the pros and cons of hiring an accountant."></div></div><p>While many believe hiring a professional is costly, it's wise to research the benefits of this option. Aside from giving you more time to focus on your business, having a numbers expert works in your favor. An accountant will allow for fewer mistakes and less time worrying if your taxes were in order.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section9-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=get-accounting-software>Get accounting software.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-get-the-right-accounting-software-for-your-needs-288x288-20200723_2023-09-25-011447_lwyo.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Get accounting software."></div></div><p>This is the more affordable option. It will require you to spend time operating an accounting system yourself, but once you find the best software for your business, you can easily do your own taxes and payroll.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section10" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>10.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=equip-and-set-up-your-coffee-shop>Equip and set up your coffee shop.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section10-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>10.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=bring-in-the-necessary-supplies>Bring in the necessary supplies.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-bring-in-the-necessary-supplies-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Bring in the necessary supplies."></div></div><p>Your coffee shop should always be equipped with the proper supplies including paper cups, dispensers, decanters, straws, and napkins. Many of these supplies are indispensable, and you will need them as much as you need a coffee grinder or an espresso machine.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section10-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>10.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=stock-up-on-utensils>Stock up on utensils.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-stock-up-on-utensils-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Stock up on utensils."></div></div><p>If you plan on making snacks and appetizers in-house, you'll need the proper kitchen utensils. This includes cutlery, coffee cups, thermometer, and milk frothers.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
