</svg>
</span><p>Basic kitchen utensils can cost between $3,000.00 to $5,000.00.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section10-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>10.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=invest-in-the-right-equipment>Invest in the right equipment.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-invest-in-the-right-equipment-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Invest in the right equipment."></div></div><p>Ensuring that you have quality equipment that works when you need it to will be crucial. Make a list of the equipment you will need and research the different brands and costs.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
