id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section12" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>12.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=host-a-grand-opening>Host a grand opening.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section12-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>12.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=plan-a-grand-opening-for-your-coffee-shop>Plan a grand opening for your coffee shop.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-have-a-grand-opening-288x288-20200817_2023-09-25-013131_zfwz.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Plan a grand opening for your coffee shop."></div></div><p>Once you've obtained the proper licensing, equipment, food, employees, and space, it's time to get to work. Your grand opening will be your introduction to the community and the final step of your coffee shop planning.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Set a date, leaving about 3-6 weeks to prepare. This gives you enough time to make final changes, gather supplies, and layout furniture.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Invest between 10% - 20% of your marketing budget for the year on your grand opening. This leaves enough room to host an event that will attract a good number of people.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Compile a press release and send it to various newspapers, media outlets, and bloggers.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Get any additional permits you may need to host your grand opening. There may also be restrictions regarding crowd size, noise level, or parking space. Make sure to double check with local laws and restrictions.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-coffee-shop-section12-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>12.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=think-about-holding-a-039-soft-opening-039-first>Think about holding a &#039;soft-opening&#039; first.</h4></div><div
